{"tid":1147184,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"【2020DSE通識】文化相對主義","createTime":"2019-05-09T16:58:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-24T17:52:21.000Z","uid":251026,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"105e321cc9b1e03aaec2b4504d93f2cdb5c16598","tid":1147184,"uid":251026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T16:58:58.000Z","msg":"文化相對主義=道德正當相對於社會文化容許嘅準則 <br />\n<br />\n西方自由主義民主非普遍適用所有社會環境，<br />\n各國有相應於自己國情嘅發展模式，各有優劣，文化相對主義係事實<br />\n<br />\n國家或社會文化之間嘅道德批判有冇準則？<br />\n民主社會不必完全無缺點，當譴責 專制社會時，至少係個方面(例如言論自由)做得好過專制社會，否則會被還擊雙重標準<br />\n<br />\nAssange爆出西方民主国家嘅war crimes，DNC操控選舉，揭發建制內不法不道德嘅行徑，今日仲要比美國建制威脅暗殺，言論出版自由已經無保護，明顯西方自由主義民主唔再擁有道德高地 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZuQW0US2sJw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DZuQW0US2sJw&d=7bK604G145JEtCxDEZ4NGrtp0LkHB2EL0pKzUaHUqTQ%3D&h=1eba9532\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZuQW0US2sJw</a>"},{"pid":"19fb0ef8e050894809510d06b4795a84238b0ca9","tid":1147184,"uid":72186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T17:38:46.000Z","msg":"国？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acc45a9af38a8cc29245bc579abbd1d27f022aaf","tid":1147184,"uid":145230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T17:52:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}